":2327730,"uid":89118,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"有一年去北海道玩，由釧路坐最晏既一班火車去知床，架火車好古老仲要得兩卡，車上人唔多，得幾個老人同學生，每個人都好安靜，四周只有火車行駛既聲音。架車好慢咁係舖滿白雪既森林中行駛，間唔中會係林木間睇到鹿群出沒，然後隨住日落整個森林都染成金黃色，果個景象真係一世難忘。"},{"pid":"dd21030f498e582cb9e2ad84a7574bf55e234360","tid":2327730,"uid":41791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0de8240d9d502e96208fdf2940fefb4719925b3e","tid":2327730,"uid":117117,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"車廂啲暖氣開到唔洗錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"1月去個陣差d焗到暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997715180d1f8f6775bad4971f4c9c2f30b230ef","tid":2327730,"uid":107687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0de8240d9d502e96208fdf2940fefb4719925b3e","tid":2327730,"uid":117117,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"車廂啲暖氣開到唔洗錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"日本啲商場都係<br />\n熱撚到"},{"pid":"95d44e334d7e6ea845afa2d97f4723f98226ec97","tid":2327730,"uid":226355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"997715180d1f8f6775bad4971f4c9c2f30b230ef","tid":2327730,"uid":107687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0de8240d9d502e96208fdf2940fefb4719925b3e","tid":2327730,"uid":117117,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"車廂啲暖氣開到唔洗錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"日本啲商場都係<br />\n熱撚到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-22T07:25:04.000Z","msg":"我同日本人返香港玩果陣佢地都覺得香港啲冷氣凍撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084f189d72e0483169dc1b04a0a8091731bb1de0","tid":2327730,"uid":49344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0